metadata.name: StonksBud #1
metadata.description: StonksBuds have no roadmap. If you own a StonkBud, you'll be part of the Stonks chat, where we share alphas, talk sh*t, play games and etc. That's pretty much all. We might do merch, we might donate to charity, it's really all gonna depend if we gonna sell out or not, to be honest.
